        <item>
            <title>2.5.8</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:22:26 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>61</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed model and effort selection not being applied to SSH remote sessions. The launcher's selection was written to the local settings file, which the CLI on the remote host never reads — remote sessions silently started with the remote default model (e.g. Sonnet instead of the selected one). The selection is now passed as `--model` / `--effort` flags on the remote command line, which also takes precedence over the remote machine's settings.
]]></description>
