        <item>
            <title>2.5.7</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 11:30:17 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>60</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Sidebar Recents no longer fills up with near-identical automated review sessions. Background sessions created by Agent SDK tools (e.g. the security-guidance plugin's per-commit security reviews, `entrypoint: sdk-py`) are now filtered out, same as `claude -p` runs. Interactive sessions are unaffected.
]]></description>
